{
  "stem": "8703.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After a beating like this, my friend, he went with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we decided-- you know, I did something which nobody did before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody-- there were people that they escaped from that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they escaped always at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At night, they thought it was safe to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the problem was, I noticed that they are-- the work-- the, the Ukrainians had dogs also.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at night, the dogs felt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If somebody-- if somebody moved around the camp, they, they caught them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what I decided, it was-- people didn't even believe that I will succeed something like that. 12 o'clock, during the day, when everybody went for lunch, including the [GERMAN], I observed them for several days.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I saw that all of them went in 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody was watching the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had lunch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of them went in to have lunch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the time we escaped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We weren't sure if they will-- if they will run after us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went to-- as a matter of fact, we found the first-- we went into the woods, through, through the forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we saw a few farmers were living over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I saw a little-- a young man coming out, about my age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I told my man-- the two men with me, I'll go in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you'll stay behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You stay one side, and the other one, another side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'll go in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'll talk to him because I want to know even where I am in the nearest town where I-- where we should go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I will talk to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I'll make signs to you because I am interested also that he should know that I am not alone.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
